 <description translatable="no">

  <p>EcotubeHQ is a streaming video player which uses AMD FidelityFX Super Resolution to play YouTube videos with enhanced quality and offers hardware acceleration to improve performance and extend the battery life of laptops.</p>
	<p>Features:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>EcotubeHQ can output hardware accelerated h.264, h.265, vp9 and av1 codecs.</li>
        <li>EcoTubeHQ offers two video output methods: 'Quality' and 'Powersave'.</li>
        <li>EcoTubeHQ restricts 720p videos to 30fps to minimize data requirements.</li>
        <li>EcoTubeHQ offers debanding to enhance video quality.</li>
        <li>EcoTubeHQ opens low resolution YouTube videos [144p / 240p] in a low bitrate miniplayer.</li>
        <li>EcoTubeHQ offers drag and drop video playlists.</li>
        <li>EcoTubeHQ can play local video files with AMD FSR upscaling.</li>
        <li>EcoTubeHQ automatically updates yt-dlp to minimize player issues.</li>
        <li>EcoTubeHQ offers two Opus audio bitrates for av1 and vp9 YouTube videos - 70kbps and 160kbps.</li>
      </ul>
 </description>
